    "art_text_section_nxVTgk": {
      "type": "art_text-section",
      "blocks": {
        "paragraph_MXUkh8": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "green_label": "",
            "white_label": "",
            "title": "From Production Innovations to New Usage Methods: Layering Up",
            "h2_text": false,
            "content": "<p>Building on these early innovations, we have developed an advanced functional layering system to meet the needs of sailors. Thanks to technological and material advancements, how technical garments are worn also becomes crucial to maximize their performance.<br\/><br\/>Our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.slam.com\/pages\/shop-by-layer\">3 LAYER SYSTEM <\/a>allows for optimal use of clothing to easily regulate comfort and protection levels based on weather conditions. The layering system consists of:<\/p><p><strong>Base Layer<\/strong>: Made from materials that keep the skin dry, promoting breathability and preventing moisture buildup.<\/p><p><strong>Middle Layer<\/strong>: Provides thermal insulation, maintaining body heat and ensuring comfort during activities in cold conditions.<\/p><p><strong>Protective Layer<\/strong>: Acts as a barrier against wind and water, protecting from the elements and keeping you dry.<\/p><p>This system is designed to offer maximum versatility and adaptability, allowing sailors to layer effectively, especially <a href=\"https:\/\/www.slam.com\/blogs\/slam-stories\/dressing-in-layers-the-perfect-solution-for-carefree-sailing\">using specific technologies that enhance garment performance<\/a>. <br\/>An example is the use of Graphene in our jackets to ensure high performance, particularly in thermoregulation, without sacrificing freedom of movement.<\/p><p><br\/> A significant improvement over heavier and bulkier past models, appreciated by sailors who value the practicality and comfort of the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.slam.com\/products\/man-active-graphene-short-jacket-a123003s00\">Active Graphene Short jacket<\/a> used as a Middle Layer even in the toughest conditions.<\/p>",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_url": "",
            "is_new_tab": false,
            "variant_color": "green",
            "truncate_text": false
          }
        }
      },
